{"tid":2064704,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旅美藝術家創「時代革命」雕塑","createTime":"2020-06-15T04:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T05:49:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5b2327011c610532c7ea8248b61d6bf796c19e75","tid":2064704,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200615/T3NZKUT4BXSC3YEHLQW5FKTF5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200615%2FT3NZKUT4BXSC3YEHLQW5FKTF5E%2F&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8jIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=ed83beeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200615%2FT3NZKUT4BXSC3YEHLQW5FKTF5E%2F&h=5fc72516\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200615/T3NZKUT4BXSC3YEHLQW5FKTF5E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n旅美藝術家創「時代革命」雕塑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】創作民主女神像的旅美雕塑家陳維明再有新作，他3月起創作以香港反送中運動為主題的大型雕塑，名為「時代革命，光復香港」，希望喚起更多大陸人關注香港的抗爭運動，作品預料在8月完成，力爭在香港雨傘運動六周年時，在美國加州「自由雕塑公園」公開展出。<br />\n<br />\n陳維明昨日在社交網站Twitter上載四張照片，雕塑上有人像高舉「罷課」、「還眼」等標語，亦刻有「五大訴求，缺一不可」的字樣，抗爭者腳踏警察盾牌，旁邊有催淚彈罐。<br />\n<br />\n陳維明寫道：「。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，很遺憾不能再次登陸和港人一起在街頭抗爭，舉牌抵擋催淚瓦斯（催淚彈），只能在美為港人的抗爭作一雕塑來紀錄並和勇敢的港人站在一起。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BISZRVLFOL47YJPYO4L67A4EEA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBISZRVLFOL47YJPYO4L67A4EEA.gif&h=9679523a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雕塑上的抗爭者手持雨傘，高舉「沒有暴徒 只有暴政」等標語。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盼大陸人關注港抗爭<br />\n<br />\n他昨向本報表示，雕塑共分為五部份，分別是時代革命、和平抗議、佔領立法會、黑警打人及光復香港，創作。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。關注香港的抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n陳維明曾經創作民主女神像、坦克人等雕塑，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。自由雕塑公園內設有連儂牆，有人貼上聲援香港、反對暴政的標語和木刻。<br />\n<br />\n陳在Twitter表示，連儂牆現時有60多塊標語和畫作，希望傘運六周年時，標語畫作增至160幅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BGWVTOMIALDAWSIE2KYRYM34ZA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBGWVTOMIALDAWSIE2KYRYM34ZA.gif&h=307a6899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自由雕塑公園的連儂牆掛上紀念港人抗爭一周年的木刻及聲援字句。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N7USVPDDPLX63UXNYW6VU7UHLM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN7USVPDDPLX63UXNYW6VU7UHLM.gif&h=5b09fbf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳維明"},{"pid":"49d477cde9bfbe7525bc228203f45a4fee5d8df8","tid":2064704,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:00:07.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/cat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/cat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d715a336917dabfe05d144e3fd7b31be553acebe","tid":2064704,"uid":83348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:11:51.000Z","msg":"好靚，哩一代抗爭手足真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e42dc36dd2bcc19e105afec44838d2bb2bfb79f","tid":2064704,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdf1b2220b7d8231dfaf8ff1340d7ef116c6660","tid":2064704,"uid":207596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6aef75275f2fe1528fdaaecf87a6205b8c1b49e","tid":2064704,"uid":225192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/flower.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/flower.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbca215aad86d190f5f63c120e6687f528157780","tid":2064704,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e82cbbfeed967451e9025f6d9ee6b3d36834061","tid":2064704,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:49:21.000Z","msg":"好想光復到再係香港展出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}